  "title": "Product Specialist",
  "description": "<h2><strong>🚀 Kickstart Your Career in IT Sales</strong></h2>\n<p>📍 <strong>Singapore</strong> | 💼 Full-Time | 💰 Basic + Commissions</p>\n<p>Are you driven, ambitious, and passionate about technology?</p>\n<p><br>\nWe’re looking for motivated individuals eager to build a career in <strong>IT sales</strong> — no prior experience in sales is required, as <strong>full training will be provided</strong>.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You’ll work with cutting-edge technology solutions, engage with clients, and learn the skills needed to succeed in a fast-paced, high-growth industry.</p>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop an understanding of our IT products &amp; solutions</li>\n  <li>Engage with potential clients via calls, emails, and meetings</li>\n  <li>Support senior sales managers in client acquisition and account management</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing sales proposals and presentations</li>\n  <li>Build relationships with partners and customers to identify opportunities</li>\n  <li>Work towards achieving sales targets and KPIs</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/Degree in any discipline (IT or Business-related advantageous)</li>\n  <li>Passion for technology and client engagement</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, target-driven, and eager to learn</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and in a team environment</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What’s In It For You</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive basic salary + commissions &amp; incentives</li>\n  <li>Structured training and mentorship</li>\n  <li>Career progression in IT sales and account management</li>\n  <li>Exposure to enterprise technology solutions and the IT distribution ecosystem</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📩 Apply now and take your first step towards a rewarding career in tech sales!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd</strong> | EA License No. <strong>20C0270</strong><br>\nEA Personnel: <strong>Tan Soon Hock (Steven)</strong> | Registration No. <strong>R1109889</strong></p>",
